{"id": 1487, "genre": 1001, "title": "你听歌时，哪些注意事项是你的“避雷针”？", "description": "为了获得更好的听歌体验，你都摸索出了哪些避免雷区的方法？（题图来自：Yasmeen Ismail ​​​​）", "record_count": 6933, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20170208152629iA13ZBFY4qyIszD8.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-02-11T17:00:25Z", "options": [{"id": 165888, "content": "跟心情不对味的", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 934361}, {"id": 168192, "content": "经典翻拍主演小鲜肉翻唱经典主题曲，彻底拉黑", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 912187}, {"id": 165633, "content": "不会听歌单，听歌组成是每日推荐+平时一直喜欢的歌曲。话说每天光听每日推荐都好多首歌，不会听不过来吗？", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 929764}, {"id": 165889, "content": "专业不是歌手唱的歌", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 912836}, {"id": 166657, "content": "徐良（声音好娘），TF，李宇春。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 936722}, {"id": 165634, "content": "用网络流行语做歌名的", "image": null, "praise_count": 167, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 794127}, {"id": 165890, "content": "某boys，某晗，某凡诸如此类，好好卖脸就可以了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 17, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 881606}, {"id": 166402, "content": "各大app热歌排行榜里面的歌", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 933008}, {"id": 166658, "content": "歌词古风，但是完全是毫无意义、堆砌词语以押韵或是让人觉得词作者特有古风，感觉很恶心", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 932328}, {"id": 167171, "content": "小清新文艺恋爱范，连前奏都受不了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 937694}, {"id": 165636, "content": "所谓的吉他弹唱 ，真是随意拨弦三两更，我来说你们听", "image": null, "praise_count": 17, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 199147}, {"id": 165637, "content": "高档次夜场全英文Club.House舞曲菲比酒吧反转Party主题高端大气上档次精品英文欧美榜单冠军电音精品重拉锯电音VIP包房至嗨house摇摆热碟", "image": "img/option/option/20170212090351l8gFeOLWn47UQjED", "praise_count":